    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "SUBJECT: UNIDENTIFIED FLYING OBJECTS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "(FLYING SAUCERS)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "At this time there appears to be no necessity for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "additional instructions for the field or insertion in the FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Handbook or Manuals relative to flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Memorandum 10-5-59 pointed out that our policy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "concerning unidentified flying objects is to conduct no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "investigation but immediately refer facts to the Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "(Bureau Bulletin Number 57, 10-1-47); that SAC Letter Number",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "38, 3-25-49, reiterated this policy and set out data desired by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Air Force to be obtained when complaint received; that SAC Letter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Number 83, 8-29-52, again pointed out our policy; that Air Force",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "on 11-12-57 assured that Bureau would be advised of any developments",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "in this field of interest to us; and that there appeared to be no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "necessity for further instructions to field or insertion in agents'",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Handbook or Manual of Instructions of our policy relating to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "During the past twelve months only one complaint",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "regarding flying saucers has been referred to the Bureau. That",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "immediately was turned over to Air Force, both in the field",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "and at the Seat of Government.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "ACTION:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "For your information. There appears to be no necessity",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "for additional instructions for the field or insertion in the FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Handbook or Manuals relative to flying saucers. This matter will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "again be reviewed on or about 10-1-61.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
